## Technical Debt

- Some layout code duplication persists between MainLayout and Dashboard; scheduled for refactoring this cycle.
- Responsive and tablet-specific behavior still needs edge-case refinement.
- A few legacy hardcoded values remain; these are being migrated to theme constants.
- Additional unit and integration tests planned for the new analytics and content modules.

